    %% ServiceAccount to ClusterRoleBinding
    SA_RHODS -->|bound via| CRB_RHODS
    SA_Dashboard -->|bound via| CRB_Dashboard
    SA_KServe -->|bound via| CRB_KServe
    SA_ODHModel -->|bound via| CRB_ODHModel
